name: Bluejohn Canyon (Main Fork)
description:
Introduction

Approach

Descent

Exit

You can exit either up the main fork or the west fork. Back up the main fork requires climbing that may be difficult for some. The West fork is the easiest exit. But you also have to take into account where you parked and how much time you have.
